<section class="slide kenBurns">
  <div class="content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="wrap">

        <div class="fix-10-12">
          <h1 class="big ae-1 fromLeft">CUE’s Online Syllabi Review Guide</h1>
          <div class="ae-2 fromLeft">
            <p class="large opacity-8">
              CUE’s tools are designed to help instructors explore and expand their agency for supporting racial equity in classroom experiences and outcomes.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fix-12-12 margin-top-5">
          <ul class="flex grid-80 fixedSpaces equal reverse">
            <li class="col-4-12">
              <div class="box-80 padding-4 equalElement left ae-3 rounded">
              <%= image_tag("graphics/syllabus-review-guide.png")%>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="col-8-12">
              <div class="box-80 padding-4 equalElement left ae-3 rounded">
                <h2 class="small text-teal">Tools for Efficacy</h2>
                <h3 class="big normal ae-5">
                  CUE’s online syllabus review guide is intended to help instructors review often taken-for-granted
                  syllabi content through a race-conscious lens and identify areas that can be leveraged to better
                  support students from minoritized racial/ethnic groups. Since the guide asks instructors to focus
                  on existing syllabi content first, it produces new, equity-serving content and language that fits
                  each unique classroom context.
                </h3>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  <div class="background" style="background-image:url(<%= image_url("patterns/png/Pattern-10.png")%>)"></div>
</section>
